==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unstate
<hw>Un*state"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>state</ets>.]</ety> <def>To deprive of state or
dignity.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>High-battled Caesar will <qex>unstate</qex> his happiness.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsteel</ent>⟦br⟧
